🚨 IMPORTANT 🚨 I had some compliments about me being in this shape all the time. But that is in fact not true, and here’s why it’s important you guys understand. I am in my best shape about 3-4 times a year. In these periods I make content to inspire you guys to reach your goals and see what’s possible. The majority of the time I’m within 3-5 weeks of achieving this shape at a higher body fat percentage. As a father, music producer, business owner, and dj I need my creativity and brain function at its maximum to succeed and enjoy life. Athletes who maintain this shape year round have my respect , but their cognitive and creative abilities are without a doubt hindered under such a stress to The Body and Brain. Dont forget that building your Body is a way to learn about discipline , structure, perseverance, and achieving goals. But, the real way you are going to gain respect, build a following, stand out amongst the world best physiques ... is to be far more than just a bodybuilder. Stay strong, Stay smart 😉 #tavicastro #bodyengineers #fatloss
